+            "&6TPS from last 1m, 5m, 15m: &f{TPS_AVG}",
+            " ",
+            "&6Memory usage: &a{MEMORY_USED}&a/{MEMORY_MAX} MB",
+            "&6Uptime: &a{UPTIME}"
